{"type":"message","id":"2625c128","parentId":"2c9b0c1b","timestamp":"2026-04-18T00:42:07.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `nvm current` command failed, indicating that `nvm` is not available in the shell environment where `exec` runs commands. This is likely the root cause of the problem: OpenClaw is being executed in a shell environment that does not have `nvm` sourced, and therefore defaults to an older Node.js version (likely a system-wide one or another in the PATH that takes precedence without `nvm`'s intervention).\n\nTo fix this, I need to ensure that the `nvm` environment is properly loaded when OpenClaw commands are executed. A common way to achieve this is to source the `nvm` initialization script before running the actual command.\n\nI'll try to execute the `openclaw gateway status` command by first sourcing the `nvm` script. I need to find the `nvm.sh` or `bash_completion` path. A typical location is `~/.nvm/nvm.sh`.\n\nI'll construct a command that sources `nvm` and then runs `openclaw gateway status`."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Descobri o problema! O `nvm` (Node Version Manager) não está sendo carregado no ambiente onde o OpenClaw está executando seus comandos. Isso significa que, embora você tenha o Node.js v22.22.2 instalado e ativo no seu terminal, o OpenClaw está usando uma versão mais antiga, provavelmente a v20.19.5, porque o `nvm` não está configurando o PATH corretamente para ele.\n\nPara resolver isso, vou tentar executar os comandos do OpenClaw forçando o carregamento do ambiente `nvm`. Vou usar um comando como este:\n\n`bash -c \"source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh && openclaw gateway status\"`\n\nIsso garantirá que o `nvm` configure o ambiente antes do OpenClaw ser executado. Se isso funcionar, podemos aplicar essa correção de forma mais permanente.\n\nPor favor, aguarde enquanto tento isso.</final>"}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":769,"output":429,"cacheRead":16802,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776472923286,"responseId":"W9PiadHbMPKHqtsPsKuhyQs"}}
